Privacy Policy
This document applies to Muviz Watch Faces, the mobile apps developed by Sparkine Labs. We've tried to keep the text simple, so we hope you will take time to read it carefully.
Personal information
We made Muviz Watch Faces with your privacy in mind, so we do not collect any personally identifiable information such as your precise geographic location, address or phone number.
Changes
We will post any privacy policy changes on this page and, if you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policies, drop us a mail at support@sparkine.com. Policy updated on 26 Jul 2024